;textarea&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tfoot\"><code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/th\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/thead\"><code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/time\"><code>&lt;time&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/title\"><code>&lt;title&gt;</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tr\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/track\"><code>&lt;track&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/tt\"><code>&lt;tt&gt;</code></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>U\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/u\"><code>&lt;u&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/ul\"><code>&lt;ul&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>V\n <ol>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var\"><code>&lt;var&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/HTML/Element/video\"><code>&lt;video&gt;</code></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>W\n <ol>\n  <li class=\"html5\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/wbr\"><code>&lt;wbr&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n </ol>\n </li><li>X Y Z\n <ol>\n  <li><s class=\"obsoleteElement\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/xmp\"><code>&lt;xmp&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></s></li>\n </ol>\n    </li>\n   </ol>\n   </details></li>\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Streszczenie","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>HTML <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> element</strong>&nbsp; <span lang=\"pl\">jest podstawowym wbudowanym kontenerem dla frazowania treści, który z natury nie reprezentuje niczego. Może być używany do grupowania tekstu w celu stylizacji</span> (używa atrybutu <code>class</code> lub <code>id</code>), <span lang=\"pl\">lub z powodu posiadania takich samych atrybutów, takich jak </span><code>lang</code>.<span lang=\"pl\"> Powinien być używany tylko wtedy, gdy nie ma zastosowania żaden inny element semantyczny</span>. <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> <span lang=\"pl\">jest bardzo podobny do elementu</span> <code>&lt;div&gt;</code>, lecz <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> jest <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Block-level_elements\">elementem blokowym</a>, a <code>&lt;span&gt;</code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Inline_elements\"> - elementem liniowym</a>.</p>\n\n<ul class=\"htmlelt\">\n <li><dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" title=\"HTML/Content_categories\">Kategorie treści</a></dfn> <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Flow content\">Flow content</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">phrasing content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Dozwolone treści</dfn><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"HTML/Content categories#Phrasing content\">Phrasing content</a></li>\n <li><dfn>Pomijanie tagów</dfn> None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</li>\n <li><dfn>Dozwolone elementy narzędne</dfn>Any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, or any element that accepts <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" title=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/HTML/Content_categories#Flow_content\">flow content</a>.</li>\n <li><dfn>Interfejs DOM</dfn> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> (before HTML 5, the interface was <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attributes","title":"Atrybuty","isH3":false,"content":"<p><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">Ten element obejmuje tylko </span><a href=\"/en-US/docs/HTML/Global_attributes\" style=\"line-height: 21px;\" title=\"HTML/Global attributes\">globalne atrybuty</a><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\">.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example1","title":"Przykład 1","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html;gutter:false notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>tekst<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result1","title":"Wynik","isH3":true,"content":"<p><span>tekst</span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example2","title":"Przykład 2","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:html;gutter:false notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>profil.html<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">target</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>_blank<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Zobacz mój profil<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>li</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"css","title":"CSS:","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p>li span {<br>\n &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; background: gold;<br>\n }</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result2","title":"Wynik","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><span style=\"background: gold;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"portfolio.html\">Zobacz mój profil</a></span></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dane_techniczne","title":"Dane techniczne","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/text-level-semantics.html#the-span-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;span&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/text-level-semantics.html#the-span-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;span&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>The DOM interface is now <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLSpanElement\"><code>HTMLSpanElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/global.html#edef-SPAN\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 Specification<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of '&lt;span&gt;' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"